{"tid":1011831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京阻見蔡英文   美國參議員：「我高興想見誰就見誰」","createTime":"2019-02-07T05:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T12:43:52.000Z","uid":79382,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8c224bf940823b7a55917293b7c2552a67d7546d","tid":1011831,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"明報：美參議員致函眾院議長　促邀請蔡英文訪華府及國會演說 (10:57)<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）周三（6日）表示，已致函眾議院議長佩洛西，促她邀請台灣總統蔡英文到訪華府，並到國會發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文去年8月過境美國得州，曾與克魯茲等政要及議員見面。克魯茲出席智庫美國企業研究所（AEI）活動時稱，北京當局此前曾寫信要求他不要與蔡英文會晤，但他回覆說「我高興想見誰就見誰」，北京無權指揮。<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲又說，台灣、日本和韓國都是美國的朋友，認為台灣對抗大陸的壓迫，對照了自由台灣與極權北京，告訴全世界哪一個是成功案例。他批評北京政府不斷施壓和圍堵台灣，維持着「虛構的一個中國政策」，認為必須加強美台關係。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190207/s00005/1549506604121/%e7%be%8e%e5%8f%83%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e8%87%b4%e5%87%bd%e7%9c%be%e9%99%a2%e8%ad%b0%e9%95%b7-%e4%bf%83%e9%82%80%e8%ab%8b%e8%94%a1%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%e8%a8%aa%e8%8f%af%e5%ba%9c%e5%8f%8a%e5%9c%8b%e6%9c%83%e6%bc%94%e8%aa%aa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190207%2Fs00005%2F1549506604121%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%258f%2583%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e8%2587%25b4%25e5%2587%25bd%25e7%259c%25be%25e9%2599%25a2%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e9%2595%25b7-%25e4%25bf%2583%25e9%2582%2580%25e8%25ab%258b%25e8%2594%25a1%25e8%258b%25b1%25e6%2596%2587%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e8%258f%25af%25e5%25ba%259c%25e5%258f%258a%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%25bc%2594%25e8%25aa%25aa&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=06059c30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190207%2Fs00005%2F1549506604121%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%258f%2583%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%2593%25a1%25e8%2587%25b4%25e5%2587%25bd%25e7%259c%25be%25e9%2599%25a2%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e9%2595%25b7-%25e4%25bf%2583%25e9%2582%2580%25e8%25ab%258b%25e8%2594%25a1%25e8%258b%25b1%25e6%2596%2587%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e8%258f%25af%25e5%25ba%259c%25e5%258f%258a%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%25bc%2594%25e8%25aa%25aa&h=1696fa4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190207/s00005/1549506604121/%e7%be%8e%e5%8f%83%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e8%87%b4%e5%87%bd%e7%9c%be%e9%99%a2%e8%ad%b0%e9%95%b7-%e4%bf%83%e9%82%80%e8%ab%8b%e8%94%a1%e8%8b%b1%e6%96%87%e8%a8%aa%e8%8f%af%e5%ba%9c%e5%8f%8a%e5%9c%8b%e6%9c%83%e6%bc%94%e8%aa%aa</a>"},{"pid":"8f23dbaf65cf0b2f23f1d36199017d8eaa334345","tid":1011831,"uid":79382,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"支那：嚴厲譴責干涉別國內政 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a433d32ad623604d95226942d3809471cde0be","tid":1011831,"uid":73804,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"ho ball"},{"pid":"cd553899839ee68487d3c8cccec6c43377105231","tid":1011831,"uid":174420,"like":2,"dislike":49,"score":-47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"美國敢唔認一個中國咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316e3aecaa9e06c24abdbb3a48d072ffc065a5e4","tid":1011831,"uid":38904,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"senator 係對 voter負責唔係支那囉好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7b09b372394b2cb34e0fa9052b803333c3384e","tid":1011831,"uid":79382,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"cd553899839ee68487d3c8cccec6c43377105231","tid":1011831,"uid":174420,"like":2,"dislike":49,"score":-47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"美國敢唔認一個中國咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"驚西咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那最叻搞小動作<br />\n例如迫航空公司改名、拍片威脅打台北<br />\n<br />\n一要做大事就瀨晒屎咁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5fb0e4f19e63297a9b106317a5d920e3368e42","tid":1011831,"uid":79382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"316e3aecaa9e06c24abdbb3a48d072ffc065a5e4","tid":1011831,"uid":38904,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"senator 係對 voter負責唔係支那囉好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:03:09.000Z","msg":"支那人緊係唔理解人哋民主點運作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af377a7b9c5f12f01ec582050ca15c9de9ce8aad","tid":1011831,"uid":64374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3da4c15dcaf78543e50c12a6250d141a3ed62c9","tid":1011831,"uid":143321,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"cd553899839ee68487d3c8cccec6c43377105231","tid":1011831,"uid":174420,"like":2,"dislike":49,"score":-47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"美國敢唔認一個中國咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:04:57.000Z","msg":"愛因斯坦有一句名言：<br />\n<br />\n「好比痲疹，民族主義是嬰兒病。」<br />\n<br />\n二十世紀最偉大的科學家愛因斯坦，從自身的經歷和體會，深深看到納粹德國煽動民族主義造成的人類禍害，也看到這種民族主義特別在年輕人當中最能發生作用，於是有以上這句名言。<br />\n<br />\n痲疹，是一種嬰兒病；同樣，民族主義也是嬰兒病。成年人極少患痲疹，而一個成熟的民族也較少受民族主義情緒鼓動，而產生盲目、衝動、排外的風潮。<br />\n<br />\n不過，民族主義與痲疹仍有不同之處，就是嬰兒時患過痲疹的人通常都會產生免疫性，痊癒後不會再患。民族主義卻不一樣，它可以一再重複地在一個不成熟的民族中發酵。<br />\n<br />\n民族主義與種族、宗教、政治認同等等有關。民族主義的產生原因很複雜，但民族主義造成的災禍卻在歷史上常見。事實上，幾乎人類有史以來的戰爭，都是民族主義戰爭。二戰時納粹德國靠宣揚日耳曼民族優越，向周邊國家發動侵略戰爭。身為德國猶太人的愛因斯坦，正是有感於這種瘋狂思潮而寫出上述那句話的。<br />\n<br />\n中國的民族主義嬰兒病，發病期有義和團運動，和文革期間的排外思潮。這種嬰兒病，直至現在仍不時發作。"},{"pid":"4b5b460e98830ebd933e84de4c50b6e63a5018ba","tid":1011831,"uid":16344,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:07:22.000Z","msg":"美國承認一個中國，一個中國係中華民國唔得㗎"},{"pid":"8f0a060a1835e240bffa104a2dfbe4791d413c89","tid":1011831,"uid":161341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c452341ba597981d24b3ea196072623d5608a603","tid":1011831,"uid":51937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbc361af0e655ccdda7a4a6d87be2274b1db664","tid":1011831,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"個參議員冇畀支共捉痛腳？"},{"pid":"f1c9848ad272c18e62e62da6c39e7489867c5a1c","tid":1011831,"uid":22624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"af377a7b9c5f12f01ec582050ca15c9de9ce8aad","tid":1011831,"uid":64374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cd553899839ee68487d3c8cccec6c43377105231","tid":1011831,"uid":174420,"like":2,"dislike":49,"score":-47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"美國敢唔認一個中國咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:51:55.000Z","msg":"呢個真，一舖貿易戰已經揭晒支那底牌"},{"pid":"da9056ad5c2f6baefdbb6f977e4d69362f6551fa","tid":1011831,"uid":85629,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"af377a7b9c5f12f01ec582050ca15c9de9ce8aad","tid":1011831,"uid":64374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cd553899839ee68487d3c8cccec6c43377105231","tid":1011831,"uid":174420,"like":2,"dislike":49,"score":-47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"美國敢唔認一個中國咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:03:16.000Z","msg